                            <comment id="257922" author="gerrit" created="Thu, 7 Nov 2019 15:26:19 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Joseph Gmitter (jgmitter@whamcloud.com) merged in patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/36615/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/36615/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
Subject: &lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LUDOC-442&quot; title=&quot;Documentation needed for LU-11213 DNE work&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LUDOC-442&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LUDOC-442&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; dne: directory creation by space/inode&lt;br/&gt;
